com.nijikokun.register.payment
Class Methods

java.lang.Object
  com.nijikokun.register.payment.Methods

public class Methods
extends Object

The Methods initializes Methods that utilize the Method interface based on a "first come, first served" basis. Allowing you to check whether a payment method exists or not. Methods also allows you to set a preferred method of payment before it captures payment plugins in the initialization process. in bukkit.yml: 

  economy:
      preferred: "iConomy"
